cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY

This paper is about stance detection, which is a natural language processing task. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with transferring knowledge across domains, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.CY (Computers and Society).
